These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
House: cape-cod, modern, art-deco, craftsman, victorian
There are 5 different favourite colors: white, turquise, apricot, lilac, fuchsia
The people have 5 different jobs:  dancer, pilot, engineer, designer, fisherman
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, baccarat, alhambra, siglo, prince
 1. the prince-smoker is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
 2. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the modern house##1
 3. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
 4. the art-deco house is the art-deco house##1
 5. the vegafina-smoker is the person who likes white##1
 6. the victorian house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
 7. the dancer is on the left of the engineer##1
 8. the craftsman house is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
 9. the craftsman house is on the far right##1
10. the cape-cod house is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
11. the victorian house is between the pilot and the person who likes fuchsia##2
12. the designer is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
13. the fisherman is on the right of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| House      | cape-cod        | modern | victorian     | art-deco   | craftsman |
| Color   | apricot     | turquise      | lilac | fuchsia   | white    |
| Job   | designer  | pilot     | dancer | engineer | fisherman  |
| Cigar           | baccarat | alhambra      | prince     | siglo   | vegafina     |

