.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, oliveros, pall-mall, game, bongani
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: skiing, soccer, golf, swimming, surfing
5 different games are played: billiard, mah-jongg, backgammon, whist, chess
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: superhero, fantasy, musical, adventure, romance
 1. the person watching romance movies is in the middle##1
 2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 3. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 4. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 5. the person watching fantasy movies is between the person playing billiard and the person who's sport is surfing##2
 6. the person watching adventure movies is the oliveros-smoker##1
 7. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 8. the person playing backgammon is the person who's sport is swimming##1
 9. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
10. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
11. the person playing backgammon is the pall-mall-smoker##1
12. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Cigar         | game | ritmeester | bongani    | oliveros  | pall-mall    |
| Sport   | surfing    | soccer       | golf      | skiing | swimming        |
| Game   | chess   | mah-jongg     | billiard    | whist  | backgammon     |
| Movie-Genre     | musical    | fantasy | romance | adventure | superhero |

