The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, december, may, august, june
 1. the person drinking coffee is the gothic-revival house##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in august is in the middle##1
 3. the townhouse house is in the middle##1
 4. the person who likes lavender is in the middle##1
 5. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 6. the person drinking water is on the left of the wooden house##1
 7. the futuristic house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 8. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
 9. the tower house is on the far left##1
10. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who likes blue##1
11. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
12. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the futuristic house##1
13. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who likes turquise and the person drinking milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Beverage         | fanta | coffee     | milk   | water   | sprite |
