.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: lemonade, iced-tea, tea, milk, sprite
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: spy, animation, horror, musical, western
The people use 5 different means of transport: snowmobile, jet-ski, quad-bike, van, bike
5 different games are played: scrabble, backgammon, domino, mah-jongg, poker
 1. the person playing backgammon is on the far left##1
 2. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 4. the person playing poker is between the person driving the van and the person drinking milk##2
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
 6. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 7. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 8. the person watching western movies is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 9. the person driving the bike is in the middle##1
10. the person driving the van is the person playing scrabble##1
11. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
12. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
13. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Beverage          | sprite  | tea     | milk   | iced-tea     | lemonade |
| Movie-Genre         | western | spy    | horror  | musical | animation   |
| Transport   | jet-ski        | snowmobile    | bike     | quad-bike     | van    |
| Game   | backgammon    | domino | mah-jongg | poker | scrabble   |

