 3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person traveling to hamburg and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
 5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the fan dubstep##1
 8. the fan folk is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1
10. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the fan reggae##1
11. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
12. the fan punk is on the left of the fan reggae##1
13. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
