.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-17::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, havana, prince, bolivar, baccarat
5 different pets are kept: snake, ferret, fish, guinea-pig, hedgehog
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: daisy, rose, sunflower, orchid, tulip
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, june, july, february, may
 1. the person who growstulip is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who growsrose##2
 2. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
 3. the havana-smoker is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 4. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 8. the owner of the fish is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
 9. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
10. the person who growssunflower is on the far left##1
11. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person who growssunflower and the owner of the fish##2
12. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
13. the prince-smoker is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Cigar    | prince       | bolivar    | baccarat | havana  | montecristo        |
| Pet       | hedgehog | snake | fish  | guinea-pig | ferret    |
| Flower       | sunflower        | orchid   | rose  | tulip   | daisy |
| Birthday   | february       | july      | may      | march | june  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, game, bluemaster, old-henry, dannemann
The people have 5 different hobbies: singing, sudoku, baking, writing, card-games
5 different games are played: domino, snooker, mah-jongg, billiard, whist
City: edinburgh, new-york, prague, paris, nizza
 1. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 2. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person who's hobby is baking##2
 3. the old-henry-smoker is the person who's hobby is writing##1
 4. the person playing whist is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
 5. the person playing domino is in the middle##1
 6. the old-henry-smoker is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person traveling to new-york##2
 7. the person traveling to paris is the bluemaster-smoker##1
 8. the tiparillo-smoker is the person traveling to prague##1
 9. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
10. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
11. the person who's hobby is baking is the person playing snooker##1
12. the person playing billiard is on the far left##1
13. the dannemann-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Cigar      | tiparillo      | game         | old-henry      | bluemaster | dannemann     |
| Hobby           | sudoku | baking | writing | card-games    | singing  |
| Game   | billiard  | snooker    | domino | mah-jongg    | whist |
| City   | prague  | new-york        | edinburgh   | paris    | nizza     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
There 5 different types of food: zucchini, peas, grapefruit, watermelon, kale
5 different games are played: domino, billiard, canasta, go, backgammon
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: azalea, dahlia, sunflower, amaryllis, bellflower
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: fantasy, horror, drama, scientific, action
 1. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
 2. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 3. the person eating kale is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 4. the person watching drama movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person who growsdahlia is between the person playing domino and the person who growsazalea##2
 6. the person playing domino is on the far left##1
 7. the person eating grapefruit is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person eating kale##2
 8. the person eating peas is between the person eating watermelon and the person eating zucchini##2
 9. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
10. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
| Food         | kale  | grapefruit | watermelon   | peas      | zucchini |
| Game   | domino   | go    | billiard | backgammon | canasta      |
| Flower           | sunflower | dahlia    | azalea       | amaryllis     | bellflower      |
| Movie-Genre     | drama | action        | fantasy  | horror        | scientific    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  accountant, bartender, freelancer, hot-chocolate-climbing, musician
City: hannover, boston, prague, colone, venice
There are 5 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, sprite, soy-milk, tea, hot-chocolate
5 different games are played: billiard, monopoly, scrabble, go, chess
 1. the accountant is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
 2. the person traveling to venice is between the person playing go and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the musician##1
 4. the person traveling to venice is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person playing chess and the person drinking soy-milk##2
 6. the person playing chess is on the right of the musician##1
 7. the person traveling to prague is the person drinking tea##1
 8. the hot-chocolate-climbing is the person drinking sprite##1
 9. the person playing billiard is the person drinking sprite##1
10. the hot-chocolate-climbing is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
11. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the bartender##1
12. the person traveling to boston is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Job         | freelancer    | musician  | bartender  | accountant      | hot-chocolate-climbing |
| City   | boston    | venice   | colone | prague | hannover   |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | iced-tea    | hot-chocolate    | tea       | sprite         |
| Game   | go  | monopoly | chess    | scrabble     | billiard      |

 